  "transcript": [
    {
      "turn": 1,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Rohan, I heard you love football and admire Messi — I’m a huge fan of his graceful style too! Tell me, did you watch any exciting matches lately? "
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Yeah, I watch match yesterday, Barcelona vs. Real Madrid. It was very close, 2-2. Messi play amazing, but he didn’t score. I think he still best player. Do you follow La Liga?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You said it perfectly that time! Good try.  \nLa Liga is exciting — I love watching Barcelona play. Who is your favorite team?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "My favorite team is Barcelona. I like their style, very attacking. Sometimes I support them even when they lose — it’s beautiful to watch. But I also like Liverpool, they play nice football too. What about you?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "I like Barcelona too — their style is so creative.  \nDo you watch any other teams in Europe?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Yeah, I sometimes watch Manchester City and Bayern Munich. They are strong teams, play smart football. Also, I follow some Indian Super League teams — like Bengaluru FC. It’s not as good as European, but I watch for fun. Do you watch football from India?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi, I enjoy watching Indian football too — it's growing!  \nDo you have a favorite player from the Indian Super League?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I think Sandesh Jhingan is very good — he is strong defender. Also, Sunil Chhetri, he is legend. You know him? I watch his matches even when they are old. He score a lot of goals. Do you know Indian players?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Nice! You're doing great — just a tiny tweak: we say \"he is a strong defender.\"  \nI love hearing about your favorites. Tell me more about Sandesh Jhingan."
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Sandesh Jhingan play for Bengaluru FC. He is very good at defending and good in the air. I think he is one of best defenders in ISL. He also play for India national team — people call him \"The Wall.\" You know, like defensive wall. Do you understand?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You're doing great! Small fix: \"he is one of the best defenders.\"  \nI get it — \"The Wall\"! That makes sense. What do you like most about his style?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 7,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "He is very calm and focused. He read the game well and make good decisions. Also, he is good with his headers — both for defending and scoring. Sometimes he score important goals, which is surprising for a defender. I think that’s why people respect him so much."
    },
    {
      "turn": 7,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You said it very well! Just a tiny tweak: \"he makes good decisions.\"  \nI agree — defenders scoring goals is exciting! Have you seen one do that live?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 8,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Yes, once. When I was in Kolkata, there was a match between Bengaluru FC and Jamshedpur FC. Sandesh scored with a header in the last minute — the stadium went wild! It was amazing to see live. Do you like surprise goals like that?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 8,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You said it perfectly!  \nLive goals are the best — they make the crowd jump! Have you watched any surprise goals from Messi?"
    }
  ],
